# {{cattag|internet|derogatory}} A bite sized [[noob]], considered by some to be worse than being a noob. Nooblets often have good grammar, but are at most times annoying, and usually seek free items in MMORPGs (Massively Multiplayer Online Role Playing Games). They usually have no clue what is going on, and need to be told many times how to complete the simplest of actions.